doctype html
html(lang='en')
    head
        meta(charset='UTF-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0')
        meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible', content='ie=edge')
        link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.8.1/css/all.css', integrity='sha384-50oBUHEmvpQ+1lW4y57PTFmhCaXp0ML5d60M1M7uH2+nqUivzIebhndOJK28anvf', crossorigin='anonymous')
        link(rel='stylesheet', href='../public/bootstrap/css/font-awesome-5.8.1.css')
        link(rel='stylesheet', href='../public/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.css')
        link(rel='stylesheet', href='../public/bootstrap/css/mdb.css')
        link(rel='stylesheet', href='../public/bootstrap/css/style.css')
        title Express EJS
    body
        // Main Navbar
        nav.navbar.navbar-expand-md.navbar-dark.bg-warning
            a.navbar-brand(href='/') Express EJS
            button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-toggle='collapse', data-target='#navbarCollapse', aria-controls='navbarCollapse', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
                span.navbar-toggler-icon
            #navbarCollapse.collapse.navbar-collapse
                ul.navbar-nav.mr-auto
                    li.nav-item
                        a.nav-link(href='/') Home
                    li.nav-item
                        a.nav-link(href='/about') About Us
                    li.nav-item.active
                        a.nav-link(href='/contact') Contact Us
                    li.nav-item
                        a.nav-link(href='/services') Services
                    li.nav-item
                        a.nav-link(href='/profile') Profile
        // Feedback Form
        .container.mb-3.mt-4
            .row
                .col-md-8.m-auto
                    .card.animated.flip
                        .card-header.bg-warning.text-white.text-center
                            h3
                                | Thanks for Your Feedback
                                span.font-weight-bold #{feedback.username}
                        .card-body.bg-light
                            ul.list-group
                                li.list-group-item
                                    | User Name :
                                    span #{feedback.username}
                                li.list-group-item
                                    | Eail :
                                    span #{feedback.email}
                                li.list-group-item
                                    | Subject :
                                    span #{feedback.subject}
                                li.list-group-item
                                    | Description :
                                    span #{feedback.description}
        // Main Content
        .jumbotron
            h1.display-4 Get in Touch
            p.lead
                | Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Ab aperiam architecto aspernatur autem dicta eos fuga in ipsam laboriosam libero natus necessitatibus obcaecati officia perspiciatis quibusdam quo, similique sint ullam vel veritatis? Culpa, distinctio dolorem eaque explicabo illum incidunt non vel. Adipisci deserunt nihil sed. Exercitationem illum maxime neque velit?
            hr.my-4
            p
                | It uses utility classes for typography and spacing to space content out within the larger container.
            a.btn.btn-warning.btn-lg(href='#', role='button') Learn more
        // Main Footer
        footer.p-3.bg-warning.text-white.text-center
            .container
                .row
                    .col
                        h3 Copyright Â© 2019 , Express Bootstrap
                        h6 All Rights Reserved
                        h6 Developed & Maintained by Express Bootstrap
        // JavaScript files for bootstrap
        script(src='../public/bootstrap/js/jquery-3.3.1.min.js')
        script(src='../public/bootstrap/js/popper.min.js')
        script(src='../public/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.js')
        script(src='../public/bootstrap/js/mdb.js')
        script.
            $('.carousel').carousel({
                interval: 1000
            })
